OL,7,F'disappointed' after a care home owner
OL,8,Fpulled out of a sale which would have
OL,9,Fseen the site used to house asylum
OL,10,Fseekers.
OL,12,FThe authority had hoped to use Ocean
OL,13,FHeights on the Isle of Sheppey to
OL,14,Fhouse unaccompanied asylum-seeking
OL,15,Fchildren.
