OL,6,FA petition, started by Karen Russon,
OL,7,Fgathered over 5 thousand signatures in
OL,8,Fa week, calling on the sale to be
OL,9,Fhalted.
OL,11,FIn the petition, Karen said: "Our
OL,12,Fbeloved town is known for its
OL,13,Ftranquility and as a popular tourist
OL,14,Fhotspot. The proposed site for the
OL,15,Fimmigration centre is next to the
OL,16,FLittle Oyster - a care home for
OL,17,Fvulnerable adults right in the heart
OL,18,Fof our community.
