OL,3,CCouncil 'disappointed' after building
OL,4,Cowner pulls out of asylum-seeker deal
OL,6,F"We fear that this project will
OL,7,Fdisrupt our peaceful environment and
OL,8,Fpotentially pose risks to our
OL,9,Fvulnerable population."
OL,11,FFollowing local pressure, its owners
OL,12,Fhave decided that the Ocean Heights
OL,13,Fsite will now be used as a care home.
OL,15,FKent County Council said it needs
OL,16,Fadditional facilities to help house
OL,17,Fthose coming into the country claiming
OL,18,Fasylum, and told ITV Meridian it was
OL,19,Fdisappointed that the sale was not
OL,20,Fgoing to go ahead.
