OL,6,F"We have been transparent about the
OL,7,Farrangements for all centres as
OL,8,Ftemporary homes for children, aged
OL,9,Funder 18, as set out on our website.
OL,11,F"Given our legal responsibilities, and
OL,12,Fthe High Court's direction, we are
OL,13,Festablishing the additional reception
OL,14,Fcentres and will identify other
OL,15,Fsuitable locations to accommodate the
OL,16,Fincreasing numbers of unaccompanied
OL,17,Fminors arriving on our shores.
